text: Andreas Lütkefels (born 19 June 1964) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Münster
